{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720820/extras/playcardcrop.gif?t=1727418882\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hexistence is a Tower Defense Deck Builder based on four universal elements: Matter, Energy, Space &amp; Time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Place powerful permanents and play wondrous spells to defend the Hexistower from the waves of mobs sent by the Void!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720820/extras/damagecrop.gif?t=1727418882\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Dynamic Card System</i>: Every card can be either played, paying its cost. Or returned to the bottom of the deck, gaining its resources which can be used to play other cards. No dead hands!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Ever-changing Map Generation</i>: Every run the map will be generated differently. Choose the path from which the mobs will take strategically so that your permanents can manage the coming waves.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>The four elements</i>: Time, Energy, Matter and Space are intertwined between them and with every aspect of Hexistence. Permanents and Mobs both have four distinct characteristics, each for every element.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720820/extras/rewardcrop.gif?t=1727418882\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720820/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1727418882","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720820/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1727418882","capsul